body_html:
thanks for the suggestion, but as I wrote, this does not work any more since rc0.12.
Every name in a graph is made unique by tensorflow, so if you create multiple summaries with the same name you end up with "_X" suffixes. It worked before because summaries used to use tags and not the names.
